00:25:28,666 --> 00:25:29,567
Kepo.

406
00:25:39,077 --> 00:25:40,245
Chúc may mắn nhé

407
00:25:43,348 --> 00:25:44,249
Tất nhiên rồi.

408
00:25:45,316 --> 00:25:46,217
